======================================================================
CONCLUSION
======================================================================

The Ω(T) structure at n=5 shows exactly which graphs arise.
H=21 is absent because no tournament on 5 vertices produces
an Ω(T) with I(Ω,2)=21.
The question remains: at what n (if any) does H=21 first appear?
